<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 03:16:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，白宫正在就让甲骨文和美国投资者接管 TikTok 进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/white-house-talks-have-oracle-us-investors-take-over-tiktok-npr-reports-2025-01-25/</link><description>根据正在谈判的交易，TikTok 的所有者字节跳动将保留该公司的股份，但数据收集和软件更新将由甲骨文监督。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 22:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/white-house-talks-have-oracle-us-investors-take-over-tiktok-npr-reports-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示可能考虑重新加入世界卫生组织</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-may-consider-rejoining-world-health-organization-2025-01-25/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普总统周六表示，他可能会考虑重新加入世界卫生组织，几天前，他因对新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 大流行和其他国际卫生危机处理不当而下令美国退出世界卫生组织。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 22:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-may-consider-rejoining-world-health-organization-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局 (CIA) 现在表示，COVID-19“更有可能”来自实验室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cia-now-says-covid-19-more-likely-have-come-lab-2025-01-25/</link><description>目前尚不清楚该机构在多大程度上收集了有关 COVID-19 起源的新情报，以及这些新证据是否用于制定最新评估。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 19:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cia-now-says-covid-19-more-likely-have-come-lab-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>上海用狗年宴庆祝农历新年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-celebrates-lunar-new-year-with-dogs-dinner-2025-01-25/</link><description>养乐多热情地咬了一口面前的鸡肉丝和生菜，然后舔了舔嘴唇。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 13:47:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-celebrates-lunar-new-year-with-dogs-dinner-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾因中国“骚扰”而暂停南海调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</link><description>菲律宾周六表示，在其两艘渔船面临中国海警和海军的“骚扰”和侵略行为后，该国已暂停在南海的一项科学调查。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 02:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>英国资深议员表示消费者和投资者希望了解中国棉花的真相</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</link><description>英国议会委员会主席周五表示，英国消费者和投资者希望了解英国在线快时尚零售商 Shein 是否销售来自中国新疆省棉花的产品的真相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>王告诉卢比奥领导人已经确定了美中关系的基调和方向</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周五与美国新任国务卿马可·卢比奥通话，北京方面表示，他告诉这位著名的对华鹰派，美中关系的方向和基调已由两国领导人确定，他希望卢比奥发挥建设性作用为了两国人民的利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:36:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾向有争议环礁的军舰发送了物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国海警表示，菲律宾周五派出一艘民用船只，向其“非法搁浅”在南海有争议环礁仁爱礁的军舰运送补给品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:25:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Shein告诉英国立法者，不允许在美国销售的产品中使用中国棉花</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</link><description>在线快时尚零售商 Shein 周五表示，要求其合同制造商只能从经批准的地区（不包括中国）采购棉花，用于在其最大市场美国销售产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>文本显示美国立法者寻求对香港进行人权制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</link><description>据路透社看到的法案文本，美国共和党和民主党议员将于周五提出一项法案，要求特朗普政府审查是否应因侵犯人权而对香港官员进行制裁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:05:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：律师称，赌博大亨因称自己为中国从事间谍活动而在泰国监狱中受到虐待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</link><description>一名被监禁的赌博大亨的律师告诉国际刑警组织，他们担心他的生命安全，他的律师告诉国际刑警组织，一名反对引渡到中国的被监禁的赌博大亨在泰国监狱中受到“不人道的待遇”，因为他声称自己是中国间谍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>泰国和中国将设立打击诈骗电话网络协调中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</link><description>泰国和中国将共同努力，打击泰国、缅甸和柬埔寨边境沿线快速增长的非法呼叫中心网络，这些呼叫中心的工作人员通常是被贩运的工人，旨在通过电话和网络诈骗来诈骗人们。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国2024年财政收入增速萎缩 非税收入跃升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-2024-fiscal-revenue-grows-13-down-64-year-earlier-2025-01-24/</link><description>财政部周五公布的数据显示，由于房地产市场持续低迷和内需放缓给经济带来压力，2024年中国财政收入同比增长1.3%，较2023年6.4%的增幅大幅放缓。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:16:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-2024-fiscal-revenue-grows-13-down-64-year-earlier-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>共同社称，中国男子因刺死日本男孩而被判处死刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</link><description>日本共同社周五援引日本驻华大使金杉贤二的话说，中国一家法院已判处一名男子死刑，罪名是在南部城市深圳刺伤一名日本男孩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>在对经济的担忧中，中国准备迎接农历新年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-readies-lunar-new-year-amid-worries-about-economy-2025-01-24/</link><description>周五，旅客们涌入火车站和机场，提着大行李箱和水果等礼物，与数百万中国人一起返回家乡，与家人一起庆祝农历新年。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-readies-lunar-new-year-amid-worries-about-economy-2025-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>